description: |
  A new command-line tool ``tmt-recipe-tool`` is available in the `teemtee/tools`__
  repository. Given a tmt recipe and its associated test results, it can produce a
  new recipe containing only the tests matching specific outcomes (e.g. ``fail``,
  ``error``, ``warn``) and optionally rerun them immediately using ``tmt``.

  __ https://github.com/teemtee/tools
